data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful home nestled on 10 acres of serene and idyllic land, offering the perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Enjoy ample space for outdoor activities, privacy, and breathtaking natural beauty that surrounds you Plus an assumable 3.5% rate.

This home boasts spacious and comfortable living areas, perfect for relaxing and entertaining guests. With attractive and functional outdoor spaces, you'll love spending time outside soaking up the sunshine and fresh air. The abundance of natural light that flows throughout the home creates a warm and welcoming atmosphere that will make you feel right at home.

Please note that the age of the residence is unknown and the buyer's agent will need to verify this information. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this tranquil oasis your own. Schedule a showing today and experience all this home has to offer!
